Zajezierze  (German Seegertswalde) is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Małdyty, within Ostróda County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south-west of Małdyty,  north-west of Ostróda, and  west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
